### Check if file contains header
```
file_has_header = has_header(table)
```
This function will return True if file has header, and false if  not. In our case:
```
True
```

```
filtered_file = csv_filter(table, 'www.ctuvaaafih.com')
```

### Convert file from csv to json  
```
csv_to_json(xsv_filename, delimiter)
```
In the same folder this function will create file named `data_file.json` with content of our csv file but in json format.
